text: Go and Get It is a 1920 American silent mystery comedy movie directed by Marshall Neilan and Henry Roberts Symonds. It stars Bull Montana, Pat O'Malley, Wesley Barry, Agnes Ayers, J. Barney Sherry, Charles Hill Mailes, Noah Beery Sr., Lydia Yeamans Titus and was distributed by First National Pictures. ==Other websites== * Category:1920s mystery movies Category:1920 comedy movies Category:American mystery movies Category:American comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Marshall Neilan
title: Go and Get It
